</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[419,509,636,662]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is named to signify that this species may already be extinct globally.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
